        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[搭建个人博客]]></title>
            <link>https://znakoa.github.io/blog/blog</link>
            <guid>https://znakoa.github.io/blog/blog</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[使用 Docusaurus 搭建个人博客网站]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>使用 Docusaurus 搭建个人博客网站</p>
<p><a href="https://docusaurus.io/zh-CN" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Docusaurus</a> 是一个静态网站生成器，它允许你使用 <strong>Markdown</strong> 和 <strong>React</strong> 来编写你的文档，然后生成一个网站。</p>
<p>Docusaurus 支持以下功能：</p>
<ul>
<li>多语言</li>
<li>丰富的主题</li>
<li>丰富的配置</li>
<li>插件系统</li>
<li>丰富的功能</li>
</ul>
<h1>搭建步骤</h1>
<ol>
<li>
<p>安装 Docusaurus CLI</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">npx @docusaurus/init@latest init my-website classic</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
<p><strong>my-website</strong> 是你项目名称，可以随便取</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>本地预览</p>
<p>使用 vscode 打开项目</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">cd my-website</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">npm run start</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="复制代码到剪贴板" title="复制" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonIcon_y97N"><path fill="currentColor" d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS"><path fill="currentColor" d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>
</li>
<li>
<p>修改配置</p>
</li>
</ol>]]></content:encoded>
